-- Sona Koyo Expects Profit Margin to Improve in Second Quarter, Kapur Says
-- Vipin Nair
-- 2010-07-28T04:23:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/sona-koyo-expects-profit-margin-to-improve-in-second-quarter-kapur-says.html

          
          
             Sona Koyo Steering Systems Ltd.
expects its profit margin to improve in the second quarter from
the previous three-month period, Surinder Kapur, Chairman, told
Bloomberg-UTV in an interview today. The company is investing
800 million rupees this year to expand facilities, he said.  
          
          


  


        